description.en: CTEChain (Career Trust Ecosystem Chain) rebuilds traditional hiring practices and is committed to creating a new hiring style where everyone is a headhunter. CTEChain subverts all recruitment platforms and human resource companies worldwide and provides a solid infrastructure for the HR industry. Its openness, ultra-high TPS, privacy protection, scalable and secure blockchain, and the adoption of many advanced innovations provide unlimited opportunities for the HR industry to serve its customers.
